title: Crackline Uganda
author: unknown
contents: A campaign in the likes of Half-Life's infamous mod "Crack-Life". It comes with a single level, that tells the player to play the vanilla game of HLM2 with the mods installed. What's the worst thing that could happen?

title: Epistle 1
author: Plank
contents: Part of the infamous "Coomtaker" saga, which hasn't been uploaded to the Steam Workshop, but instead on The Workshop Labs' Discord server, since its ending crashes the game no matter which way you go.
